Name: 1 & Winterfold Rd, Hamilton Hill
Risk Third: Vehicles travel over the speed limit
Description: Turning left (west) into winterfold rd from travelling north on Stock rd is dangerous. There is no turning lane on the left, the small amount of lane is at a poor angle so when you look to the right it is very hard to see oncoming traffic. Lot of cars also fail to reduce to the 60kmh speed limit on Winterfold. On the other side of this intersection near Seton College, 2 lanes quickly reduce into one then a roundabout, This should have 2 lanes continued further beyond Seton. Traffic banks up quik
